{"title":"五一的五一  为一九五一年五月一日北京五一劳动节示威游行大会作","authors":["黄炎培"],"dates":[{"year":1951,"month":5,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"五一的五一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为一九五一年五月一日北京五一劳动节示威游行大会作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄炎培"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是中国的红场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是世界最大的首都广场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"静荡荡！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不见有一点灰尘在飞扬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只从无数面红旗影里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"透露出一曲一直的红墙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片晴光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片红光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绝没有行人来往。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只剩着五座圜桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俯伏着；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两座华表，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耸立着。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们都悄悄地屏着气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等候那动员令下降。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轰隆！轰隆，轰隆！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十八响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声一声发出来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都从那已经在两年前赶走了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义的东交民巷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六十万人五一劳动节示威大游行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就这样开场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最先出场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是文工大队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几百千个腰鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编成了方形，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟着节拍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且鼓且舞地展开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接上来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切一切，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五花八门地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有声有色地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一队一队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都须通过一条视线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这视线发自天安门游行检阅的高台。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽然从人群里放出和平鸽子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一大群向着天空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞！飞！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一头飞上了天安门楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恰和检阅台郭沫若先生相对，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咕！咕，咕！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛在唤着："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“和平！和平！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的郭老！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我和你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家飞去又飞来。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于得到了郭老的点头神会。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这队伍中间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"占着多数的是市民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"充分表现出热诚而又天真的神态："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颠一拐的老汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过了天安门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步一回头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不断地致敬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着主席台"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝着神，像发呆；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲们去年在队里还抱着婴孩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年不抱了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为的是每一条巷子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组织了临时托儿所，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在代替她喂奶；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一大群和尚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一大群尼姑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都跟着喊口号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们和她们都在搞生产，能自立了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只在婚姻问题上，还是除外。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最后是机关队伍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"很有意义的是末了一幅旗帜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“抗美援朝总会”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前前后后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片声像狂潮，像怒雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“中华人民共和国万岁！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“毛主席万岁！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一座泰山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巍巍地耸立在天安门楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一轮太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着四面八方放出了温暖的气流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马克思，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列宁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斯大林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一百多年来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的发明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辉煌的成就，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靠了他，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"替我们找出了正确的枢纽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靠了他，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带我们向着光明的大道走！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是写新民主主义者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写实践论者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是思想的导师。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是一般的政治领袖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更不只是文章妙手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请看天安门楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一大群民主党派代表，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民革，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民盟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民建，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有无党无派的社会名流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"统一战线早已成立了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像众星环拱着北斗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“中国出了一个毛泽东”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民歌早唱遍了二十世纪地球上五个大洲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（四）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动创造了世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是世界人们还没有认识，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连劳动者自己也没有认识得亲切。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哲人把真理揭穿了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动者站起来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是还存在着不少不少当前的强敌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了团结世界工人阶级，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了争取世界工人胜利团结，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在六十二年以前，（一八八九年）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公定了每年五月一日国际劳动节。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是新中国的“五一”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"意义还不只这些，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的劳动者已经胜利了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华人民共和国统一战线的政权，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"基础是工农联盟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领导者是工人阶级。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"垂死的帝国主义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野心还不肯断绝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔着渤海湾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屡战屡败的美帝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还在不断地挣扎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这正值得提高警惕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要加紧生产。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要加强团结。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管是体力劳动者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脑力劳动者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工作领导者。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一分力，献一分力。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记着！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这不是寻常地一般地五一劳动节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它将从欢欣中提起警觉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将从庆祝中带来鞭策。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"意义多么深长呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这才是一九五一年的五一，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五一的五一。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}